prompts.frontCover: Greeting card front cover, anniversary theme. A romantic cartoon-style illustration of a man and a woman relaxing together at a beach picnic during a magnificent sunset. They are sitting close on a large, soft woven blanket, leaning against each other in a sweet, loving pose. They are sipping from unique boba tea drinks served in hollowed-out coconut shells, complete with large boba straws. The scene is framed by lush, tropical botanical elements like large monstera leaves, palm fronds, and delicate hibiscus flowers in shades of coral and white, creating a natural border that enhances the composition. The beach is serene with soft, pale sand. In the background, the sun is a glowing orb, casting a warm, golden-orange and soft pink light across the sky and the calm ocean waves. In the center, in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script, is the text "Happy Anniversary, my love". Flat 2D vector illustration, clean lines, warm and romantic color palette, charming and intimate atmosphere.
